{"tid":1717181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班暴徒有書都冇得讀！","createTime":"2019-11-13T14:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T14:40:21.000Z","uid":15133,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1e539f8b85cd15edf31dde8bb8de99da4dc5b76c","tid":1717181,"uid":15133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:08:45.000Z","msg":"咁就要好好利用課餘時間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾間u都set好防線<br />\n可以利用時間黎開不同班<br />\n教授不同技能<br />\n好似 掟下野、衝向前、射下野既pe堂 <br />\n仲有做實驗既phy chem堂<br />\n最好練埋做人最缺少既勇氣<br />\n<br />\n上完唔同班 仲可以小班出去搵下地方實習<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n記得天琦講過 <br />\n佢當有諗過個口號係世代革命 定 時代革命<br />\n佢揀時代既原因係<br />\n時代無分年齡<br />\n就算年紀多\u001d大<br />\n只要是相信自由<br />\n擁抱自由，就是屬於新時代！<br />\n<br />\n另外 切記雨革教訓 唔好嘉年華化！"},{"pid":"5d8a8c53f5a8de1585afae590b210448e7de15c6","tid":1717181,"uid":15133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1mu3GGq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1mu3GGq.jpg&h=81b693da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6276e272d19e054529921f6cc57c1f995a789232","tid":1717181,"uid":15133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qkd78my.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqkd78my.jpg&h=84f6a47a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd71823bf44a276d7003cbf9f1fc78136d5c46d1","tid":1717181,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932f27c01b5c8769fa1ac4fce5e8c325d4a15cca","tid":1717181,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />